# API Testing Specification

This specification demonstrates API testing using JSONPlaceholder API

## Get and Create Posts
Tags: api, posts

* Get all posts from JSONPlaceholder
* Verify get posts response status code is "200"
* Get a specific post with id "1"
* Verify the post title contains "sunt aut facere"
* Create a new post with title "Test Post" and body "This is a test post"
* Verify post creation status code is "201"
* Verify created post contains correct title "Test Post"
